             was indicted for <rs id="t18290409-240-off1353" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18290409-240-off1353" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18290409-240-off1353" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18290409-240-cd1354" type="crimeDate">17th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290409-240-off1353 t18290409-240-cd1354"></join>, 1 handkerchief, value 3s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18290409-240-victim2250" type="victimName">
                           John White 
                           Welch
                        <interp inst="t18290409-240-victim2250" type="surname" value="Welch"></interp>
